---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl p-6 space-y-6">
    <header class="text-center mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400">Effective Date: December 9, 2025</p>
    </header>

    <div class="max-w-none space-y-6 text-slate-300">
      <div class="bg-slate-900/60 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          MintLoop, LLC d/b/a MintLabs ("Company," "we," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you use the Lucky Number Generator (the "Service").
        </p>
      </div>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We do not collect personal information unless you provide it voluntarily (e.g., through a contact form).</p>
        <p class="mt-3">We may automatically collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> (pages viewed, clicks, time on site).</li>
          <li><strong>Device and browser data</strong> (IP address, operating system, referral URL).</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies and tracking technologies</strong> for analytics and advertising.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>What We Do NOT Collect or Store:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Fictional Currency Balances:</strong> No fictional currencies (e.g., "MintyCatnipCoin") are tracked, stored, or associated with user accounts. They exist only as browser-based demonstrations.</li>
          <li><strong>Casino-Lite Simulation Results:</strong> All simulated card games, dice rolls, wheel spins, and raffle picks execute locally in your browser. No results, bets, or play history are sent to servers.</li>
          <li><strong>Microtool Inputs:</strong> Wheel spinner segments, raffle participant names, calculator inputs, and custom settings remain client-side unless you explicitly save/share results.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> We do not process payments or store financial data. The Service is free and does not sell products.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Use of Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected data to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Operate and improve the Service.</li>
          <li>Monitor traffic and usage patterns.</li>
          <li>Display relevant advertising (e.g., Google AdSense).</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Specific Uses:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Analyzing tool usage patterns to improve user experience and identify popular features.</li>
          <li>Monitoring performance metrics to optimize page load times and responsiveness.</li>
          <li>Detecting and preventing abuse, automated scraping, or security threats.</li>
          <li>Sending voluntary newsletter subscriptions or responding to contact form inquiries.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Data Minimization:</strong> We collect only what is necessary for Service operation. We do not profile users, build behavioral models for advertising, or track individual gambling/gaming patterns.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Advertising and Third Parties</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>We may display ads through Google AdSense or similar networks. These third parties may use cookies to serve personalized ads.</li>
          <li>You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting: <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.google.com/settings/ads</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Third-Party Services:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> May place cookies to serve personalized or contextual ads. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Providers:</strong> May collect anonymized usage data. We do not share personally identifiable information with analytics providers.</li>
          <li><strong>No Social Media Tracking:</strong> We do not embed Facebook Pixel, Twitter tracking, or similar social media surveillance tools.</li>
          <li><strong>No Third-Party Access to Tool Inputs:</strong> Your wheel spinner segments, raffle names, and calculator inputs are not shared with ad networks or analytics providers.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share limited data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Service providers</strong> (analytics, hosting).</li>
          <li><strong>Legal authorities</strong> if required by law.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>We Do NOT:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Sell, rent, lease, or trade user data to third parties.</li>
          <li>Build gambling behavior profiles or "problem gambler" identification models.</li>
          <li>Share microtool usage patterns with advertisers or data brokers.</li>
          <li>Monetize fictional currency activity or simulation tool engagement.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Cookies are small files stored on your device. You may block cookies in your browser, but some features may not function properly.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Cookie Types:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Session management, security features, and user preferences. These are necessary for Service operation.</li>
          <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Usage tracking, page views, and performance monitoring. Duration: typically 1-2 years.</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> Third-party ad network cookies for personalized or contextual ads. Duration: varies by provider.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Local Storage:</strong> We may use browser local storage for theme preferences, tool settings, and educational content progress. This data never leaves your device.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain data only as long as necessary for Service operation and legal compliance:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> Aggregated usage metrics retained indefinitely for trend analysis. Individual session data typically expires after 1-2 years.</li>
          <li><strong>Newsletter Subscriptions:</strong> Email addresses retained until you unsubscribe. Unsubscribe links included in all emails.</li>
          <li><strong>Contact Form Submissions:</strong> Retained for 3 years for customer support and legal compliance.</li>
          <li><strong>Tool Inputs and Results:</strong> Not stored on servers. All microtool data (wheel spinner, raffle picker, casino-lite simulations) executes client-side and is never transmitted or retained.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Data Deletion:</strong> To request deletion of voluntarily provided information (email, contact form), email privacy@mintloop.dev with your request.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>The Service is not directed to individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">8. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We use reasonable measures to protect information, but no system is completely secure. Use of the Service is at your own risk.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">9. International Use</h2>
        <p>If you access the Service from outside the United States, you consent to the processing and storage of your information in the U.S.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Jurisdiction-Specific Rights:</strong></p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>GDPR (EU/EEA):</strong> You may have rights to access, rectification, erasure, and data portability under the General Data Protection Regulation. Contact privacy@mintloop.dev to exercise these rights.</li>
          <li><strong>CCPA (California):</strong> California residents may request disclosure of data collection practices and request deletion of personal information. We do not sell personal information as defined by CCPA.</li>
          <li><strong>Other Jurisdictions:</strong> Users in other regions should review local data protection laws. We make reasonable efforts to comply with applicable regulations but cannot guarantee compliance with all international laws.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>Gambling Restrictions:</strong> If your jurisdiction prohibits online gambling simulations or fictional gaming tools, you are responsible for compliance. We do not verify user locations or enforce regional gambling restrictions.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes are effective upon posting. Continued use of the Service indicates acceptance.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">11. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related questions:</p>
        <div class="bg-slate-900/60 p-4 rounded-lg mt-2">
          <p class="font-semibold">MintLabs / MintLoop</p>
          <p>Email: <a href="mailto:privacy@mintloop.dev" class="text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300">privacy@mintloop.dev</a></p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
        <img src="/clover.png" alt="Lucky Clover" class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
        Generate Numbers
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
